{"tid":1297753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"714 倫敦響應 do you hear the people sing作詞人 Sing for HK","createTime":"2019-07-08T16:34:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T00:46:30.000Z","uid":27987,"like":225,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"9e4588892c828a85aac7d2e4fd1b05eee54c748c","tid":1297753,"uid":27987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:34:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Do you hear the people sing 既lyricist Herbert Kretzmer 6月19日係Daily Mail UK 寫左一篇文章 係關於香港人最近既行動同佢首歌既關連</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其中佢講左句 一直有留意香港既情況 佢都係倫敦睇住電視同我地一齊唱住呢首歌</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有見及此 為左響應佢既說話 聲援香港 倫敦今個星期日將會有Sing for HK 活動 係街頭唱do you hear the people sing, imagine, free the people等等幾首歌 希望大家可以幫手宣傳！ #國際關注 #singforhk<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/366370414066734/?ti=icl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F366370414066734%2F%3Fti%3Dicl&d=QWAfKg5qpFwl7mzrwQ2WUosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=698cc20e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/366370414066734/?ti=icl</a><br />\n<br />\n希望其他國家/城市都可以做類似既事 唔好頹 抖左陣快啲起身再黎過啦有好多野可以做架。<br />\n<br />\n佢寫果篇文既link<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-7160409/How-humbling-Les-Miserables-hit-helped-fight-freedom.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-7160409%2FHow-humbling-Les-Miserables-hit-helped-fight-freedom.html&d=QWAfKg5qpFwl7mzrwQ2WUosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=64e6b7ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-7160409/How-humbling-Les-Miserables-hit-helped-fight-freedom.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" cla